        dependencies among IHE IT Infrastructure Integration Profiles.
        The arrows in the figure point from a given integration profile
        to the integration profile(s) upon which it depends. Table 2-1
        defines these dependencies in tabular form.
      </para>
      <para>
        Some dependencies require that an actor supporting one profile
        be grouped with one or more actors supporting other integration
        profiles. For example, Enterprise User Authentication (EUA)
