    <section xml:id="xds-sd-actor-options">
      <title>XDS-SD Actor Options</title>
      <para>
        Options for Scanned Documents leverage those in the IHE Patient
        Care Coordination Technical Framework (PCC TF). Options that may
        be selected for this Integration Profile are listed in the Table
        20.3-1 along with the Actors to which they apply. Dependencies
